import React from "react"
import { Box } from "@mui/system"
import { Button, Container } from "@mui/material"

export default function Homepage(){

    return(
        <Box sx={{
            display:'flex',
            flexDirection: 'column'
        }}>
            <Box>
                <Container>
                    <Button>Manual mode</Button>
                </Container>
            </Box>
            <Box>
                <Container>
                    <Button>Follow mode</Button>
                </Container>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    )
}
